Package: agent-ros-bridge
Version: 0.5.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv
Recommends: redis-server, postgresql
Maintainer: Agent ROS Bridge Team <team@agentrosbridge.io>
Description: Universal interface for AI agents to control ROS robots
 Agent ROS Bridge provides a natural language interface for controlling
 ROS1 and ROS2 robots. It supports multiple AI frameworks including
 OpenClaw, LangChain, AutoGPT, and MCP.
 .
 Features:
  - Natural language robot control
  - Multi-robot fleet management
  - Context-aware conversations
  - Safety and validation
  - Autonomous behaviors
Homepage: https://github.com/webthree549-bot/agent-ros-bridge
